						               													<description>Death Dome is an action strategy game where you control a team of four units inside the Death Dome battleground. The objective of each match is to use your team to capture as many control points and gather as many credits as possible. Between matches, you must equip your team with the best equipment that you can afford.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Play a quick match or a whole campaign series. Try different combinations of characters and equipment. Capture control points, collect beetle shells for defeating enemy units, and free your teammates from jail if they are captured.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players start with 4 units in a base and get to move 2 units each turn. The match lasts for 6 turns. Each unit phase a unit can move and do 1 action, usually either capture a control point or attack an enemy unit. Players get points for each captured control point or defeated enemy at the end of the match. The player with the most points wins. Points turn into credits and can be used to buy new equipment for the next match. Players can compete in a series of matches.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players draw cards each turn, with bonus cards for each 5 control points they control. Cards can be used to attack or defend or other abilities. Cards are only redrawn at the start of each turn so players must decide how to manage their hand of attacks and save some for defense.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher's website&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
